RT @ZJemptv: Putting it all in context: http://t.co/KhkIMZAe #trans #girlslikeus
Kicked out of a bar last night. Had nothing to do with status. But my drunk mind made that connection and it shouldn't have. #girlslikeus
And #girlslikeus shouldn't be a cognitive category; just an existential reality: we are who we are, no one else, no one less.
